5:

12:
That will more than do. In fact, I

15:
Apologies, but I'll send someone else

make another visit and seek out
other options as well.
18: I am extremely grateful for your aid.
29:
Thanks, Ariel... I feel a bit better. Think
the last medicine you brought is

34:

96:

116:
Could you bring that Lilith and your

188:
Hmm, I see what he meant now by

191:
Gwynn, frail mortal that you were...

eternity you sought.
